sentence: In early trading on Thursday, shares of Boeing ( BA ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.5%.
Year to date, Boeing registers a 15.2% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is General Electric ( GE ), trading down 1.3%.
General Electric is lower by about 7.0% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Home Depot ( HD ), trading down 0.4%, and Intel ( INTC ), trading up 1.4% on the day.
